WEBVTT

00:01:36.959 --> 00:01:38.200
Normally,

00:01:38.480 --> 00:01:40.319
I really wish I could step on you a couple of times.

00:01:40.760 --> 00:01:42.799
But when I see you at the end of your rope,

00:01:42.959 --> 00:01:44.359
I hope you can get back on your feet.

00:01:45.280 --> 00:01:47.319
Just look at society today.

00:01:47.680 --> 00:01:50.599
People who can truly let their guard down and be honest

00:01:50.719 --> 00:01:53.120
seem to be just the few of us.

00:01:53.120 --> 00:01:54.599
The ones who grew up together.

00:01:59.079 --> 00:02:01.319
So, you have feelings for me?

00:02:02.480 --> 00:02:03.439
No, no, no.

00:02:03.560 --> 00:02:05.000
We're really not a good match.

00:02:05.239 --> 00:02:06.159
Ugh, please.

00:02:06.959 --> 00:02:08.960
Don't flatter yourself.

00:02:09.439 --> 00:02:10.319
I'm doing it out of

00:02:10.319 --> 00:02:12.759
our three-generation-old neighborhood ties.

00:02:12.960 --> 00:02:15.039
Most importantly, I want to help Big Brother.

00:02:15.280 --> 00:02:16.280
What do you mean?

00:02:18.439 --> 00:02:20.080
What I mean is,

00:02:20.800 --> 00:02:22.439
if you're really in trouble,

00:02:22.719 --> 00:02:25.080
just say the word, and I'll do what I can.

00:02:25.520 --> 00:02:27.599
Third Uncle, I'm starting to realize

00:02:27.599 --> 00:02:29.240
you're really not an ordinary person.

00:02:29.360 --> 00:02:31.360
To be honest before,

00:02:31.360 --> 00:02:33.280
I thought some of your actions

00:02:33.800 --> 00:02:34.919
were pretty strange.

00:02:35.120 --> 00:02:36.080
But now,

00:02:36.080 --> 00:02:37.319
it's made me understand a principle.

00:02:37.319 --> 00:02:38.319
Wise people,

00:02:38.319 --> 00:02:39.919
are often misunderstood.

00:02:40.039 --> 00:02:41.639
So, for our second treatment session,

00:02:41.639 --> 00:02:42.840
are you still willing to trust me?

00:02:42.840 --> 00:02:43.639
Of course.

00:02:43.840 --> 00:02:44.520
Third Uncle.

00:02:44.520 --> 00:02:46.759
How do you plan to treat me?

00:02:48.080 --> 00:02:50.240
You can't possibly get me expelled from school, right?

00:02:51.000 --> 00:02:53.400
I'll teach you to think independently.

00:02:53.400 --> 00:02:55.599
Teach you how to get along with your dad.

00:02:55.840 --> 00:02:56.840
Instead of arguing all day

00:02:56.840 --> 00:02:58.400
and talking at cross-purposes.

00:02:58.599 --> 00:03:00.080
He needs to see you've matured,

00:03:00.080 --> 00:03:02.120
not acting willful and throwing tantrums.

00:03:02.400 --> 00:03:04.080
Then he'll naturally trust your choices.

00:03:05.759 --> 00:03:07.159
So when do we start?

00:03:07.560 --> 00:03:08.479
Don't rush.

00:03:09.520 --> 00:03:12.240
Chunsheng, dinner's ready!

00:03:15.560 --> 00:03:16.840
I've been calling you for dinner.

00:03:16.840 --> 00:03:17.840
All this time,

00:03:17.840 --> 00:03:19.439
couldn't you answer?

00:03:19.639 --> 00:03:20.879
I just heard you now.

00:03:20.879 --> 00:03:22.039
Almost done wiping this.

00:03:23.360 --> 00:03:27.479
Hey, Second Brother hasn't been around for a few days.

00:03:27.479 --> 00:03:29.159
He's not holding a grudge, is he?

00:03:30.280 --> 00:03:32.159
Over such a small thing? He wouldn't, right?

00:03:32.159 --> 00:03:33.240
Why wouldn't he?

00:03:33.240 --> 00:03:34.960
Second Brother wanted to go into business with you.

00:03:34.960 --> 00:03:35.840
Wasn't that a good thing?

00:03:35.840 --> 00:03:37.120
You had to shut him down.

00:03:37.120 --> 00:03:38.520
What good thing?

00:03:38.680 --> 00:03:41.159
Isn't it better to live a steady life?

00:03:41.840 --> 00:03:43.919
Starting a business isn't that easy.

00:03:44.120 --> 00:03:44.840
Let me tell you,

00:03:44.840 --> 00:03:45.680
this Second Brother,

00:03:45.759 --> 00:03:47.599
he's just been provoked.

00:03:48.159 --> 00:03:49.919
His wife ran off with someone.

00:03:50.000 --> 00:03:51.479
He just wants to prove himself.

00:03:51.479 --> 00:03:53.599
No, shouldn't you help him even more then?

00:03:53.599 --> 00:03:55.759
You brothers should prove yourselves together.

00:03:55.759 --> 00:03:56.840
Stand up for him.

00:03:56.840 --> 00:03:58.599
But is that really standing up for him?

00:03:58.599 --> 00:04:00.240
Wouldn't that be harming him?

00:04:00.360 --> 00:04:02.919
Second Brother has been competitive since he was a kid.

00:04:03.560 --> 00:04:05.120
If I don't hold him back a bit,

00:04:05.199 --> 00:04:07.960
he'd put his entire life savings into it.

00:04:09.080 --> 00:04:10.479
Big Brother, Sister-in-law.

00:04:10.680 --> 00:04:11.120
Weiguo.

00:04:11.120 --> 00:04:11.719
Weiguo.

00:04:11.960 --> 00:04:13.360
Have you eaten? Join us.

00:04:13.360 --> 00:04:14.120
I've eaten.

00:04:14.240 --> 00:04:15.319
I wanted to talk to you about

00:04:15.319 --> 00:04:16.879
Feifei's next phase.

00:04:16.879 --> 00:04:17.959
Let me tell you,

00:04:17.959 --> 00:04:19.240
Feifei has been

00:04:19.240 --> 00:04:21.000
much more stable lately.

00:04:21.120 --> 00:04:22.920
But you haven't made a move.

00:04:23.079 --> 00:04:24.759
I just spent some time preparing.

00:04:25.279 --> 00:04:27.600
So there's going to be a big move?

00:04:27.600 --> 00:04:29.120
But I need your cooperation, Big Brother.

00:04:29.120 --> 00:04:30.959
Cooperate, cooperate. How?

00:04:30.959 --> 00:04:32.720
I need you to ask for a few days off for Feifei.

00:04:33.639 --> 00:04:35.000
A few days off?

00:04:36.600 --> 00:04:37.639
To do what?

00:04:37.800 --> 00:04:39.079
You'll know when the time comes.

00:04:45.959 --> 00:04:47.199
Are you setting me up?

00:04:49.519 --> 00:04:53.000
Look, just think of it as us doing a deal.

00:04:53.680 --> 00:04:55.720
Doing business always involves some risk.

00:04:56.360 --> 00:04:57.680
Just say the word.

00:05:07.800 --> 00:05:10.519
Alright, I'll go all in.

00:05:15.920 --> 00:05:17.920
I... I am indeed in trouble.

00:05:18.839 --> 00:05:20.319
If you can lend a hand,

00:05:20.480 --> 00:05:22.360
then I really must thank you properly.

00:05:25.480 --> 00:05:26.279
Lianbao.

00:05:27.120 --> 00:05:30.319
We've been rivals for half our lives.

00:05:31.040 --> 00:05:33.959
This time, we finally laugh and let bygones be bygones.

00:05:35.240 --> 00:05:37.120
Actually, I just wanted to hear you say one thing.

00:05:56.879 --> 00:06:01.079
I went too far before.

00:06:01.920 --> 00:06:03.319
I'm sorry.

00:06:08.759 --> 00:06:10.279
Actually, all these years,

00:06:10.839 --> 00:06:12.079
towards you,

00:06:12.680 --> 00:06:14.360
I haven't been without feelings.

00:06:15.480 --> 00:06:18.319
It's just, I could never say it out loud.

00:06:19.639 --> 00:06:21.160
You might not even know,

00:06:22.279 --> 00:06:24.360
ever since I was in third grade,

00:06:24.680 --> 00:06:26.360
I wanted to be with you...

00:06:32.000 --> 00:06:33.240
No, what are you laughing at?

00:06:38.920 --> 00:06:39.839
You said it yourself.

00:06:49.759 --> 00:06:53.920
"I went too far before."

00:06:54.759 --> 00:06:56.160
"I'm sorry."

00:06:56.160 --> 00:06:56.879
Well?

00:06:57.439 --> 00:07:00.439
I recorded everything you just said.

00:07:00.639 --> 00:07:02.240
"I cherish this bond."

00:07:02.240 --> 00:07:03.959
You're so treacherous!

00:07:05.839 --> 00:07:06.879
Let me tell you,

00:07:07.000 --> 00:07:09.120
if I don't crush you completely,

00:07:09.240 --> 00:07:10.680
I'd be letting myself down.

00:07:12.040 --> 00:07:13.480
Li Lianbao, listen up.

00:07:13.680 --> 00:07:15.720
I'll give you one chance now.

00:07:15.959 --> 00:07:17.439
Go back and persuade Big Brother properly

00:07:17.439 --> 00:07:18.759
to cooperate with me.

00:07:18.759 --> 00:07:20.160
If he agrees,

00:07:20.480 --> 00:07:23.279
maybe I'll delete this recording.

00:07:25.759 --> 00:07:27.560
So you're still scheming.

00:07:27.720 --> 00:07:29.480
Still coveting Peng Le Xuan.

00:07:29.639 --> 00:07:32.240
Well? Think it over carefully.

00:07:42.360 --> 00:07:43.360
Listen carefully.

00:07:44.600 --> 00:07:46.439
I'll throw away my pride.

00:07:47.000 --> 00:07:48.360
If I can't fight you to the death,

00:07:48.480 --> 00:07:50.000
I'll fight until I die trying.

00:07:50.639 --> 00:07:51.759
I refuse to believe

00:07:52.199 --> 00:07:54.319
that I can't accomplish what I set out to do.

00:07:56.560 --> 00:07:58.199
I wish you immediate success.

00:08:08.800 --> 00:08:11.319
Director Li, the talk didn't go well, huh?

00:08:12.160 --> 00:08:13.000
Just so-so.

00:08:14.160 --> 00:08:14.839
What's wrong?

00:08:15.480 --> 00:08:16.759
You didn't... with her?

00:08:16.759 --> 00:08:17.720
I... with her?

00:08:17.879 --> 00:08:19.000
She... with me.

00:08:19.240 --> 00:08:20.240
Alright, let's not talk about it.

00:08:20.240 --> 00:08:22.240
So what do we do next?

00:08:23.000 --> 00:08:24.000
It's already come to this.

00:08:24.240 --> 00:08:25.279
I'm going all in.

00:08:25.839 --> 00:08:27.920
Let's go, we're heading to Old Xie's place.

00:08:48.960 --> 00:08:51.159
Uncle, where exactly are we going?

00:08:51.559 --> 00:08:53.840
To the countryside, deep into the mountains.

00:08:55.320 --> 00:08:56.759
To remember past hardships and appreciate present sweetness?

00:08:57.519 --> 00:08:58.600
You'll find out in a moment.

00:09:16.840 --> 00:09:17.799
This is the place?

00:09:18.720 --> 00:09:20.480
They're all waiting up there. Everything's arranged.

00:09:20.480 --> 00:09:21.360
Come up with me.

00:09:30.440 --> 00:09:31.720
The village conditions now...

00:09:31.720 --> 00:09:32.879
are much better than before.

00:09:32.879 --> 00:09:35.039
There's running water, electricity, and even internet.

00:09:35.639 --> 00:09:37.360
From here to the town bus station...

00:09:37.360 --> 00:09:38.600
it's only one kilometer.

00:09:39.159 --> 00:09:41.440
Our village can even order takeout now.

00:09:41.759 --> 00:09:43.960
The child definitely won't suffer here.

00:09:44.600 --> 00:09:47.000
Next year, there'll even be a park in the east end of the village.

00:09:47.360 --> 00:09:49.000
The environment is really nice.

00:09:49.879 --> 00:09:51.960
Look, look, it's this house.

00:09:52.279 --> 00:09:53.399
Right here, right here.

00:09:55.879 --> 00:09:56.519
Let's go.

00:10:04.600 --> 00:10:07.039
Granny, he doesn't need to do farm work.

00:10:07.399 --> 00:10:09.360
Remember, don't let him eat meat.

00:10:09.360 --> 00:10:11.000
Keep a close eye on the chickens at home.

00:10:11.000 --> 00:10:12.360
Count them every single night.

00:10:12.799 --> 00:10:14.039
Okay, okay, okay.

00:10:14.039 --> 00:10:15.320
Uncle, I...

00:10:15.759 --> 00:10:17.600
You're really going to leave me here alone?

00:10:18.000 --> 00:10:18.759
Weiguo.

00:10:19.200 --> 00:10:21.200
Maybe we should try a different approach.

00:10:21.600 --> 00:10:22.879
Big Brother, you promised me.

00:10:22.879 --> 00:10:24.480
You said you'd listen to whatever I say.

00:10:28.039 --> 00:10:28.840
Fine.

00:10:29.519 --> 00:10:31.600
A gentleman's word is his bond, right?

00:10:33.600 --> 00:10:35.480
Then I'll wait for you outside.

00:10:43.120 --> 00:10:43.840
Have some water.

00:10:44.000 --> 00:10:44.600
No, thank you.

00:10:44.600 --> 00:10:45.279
Dad.

00:10:46.879 --> 00:10:47.559
Dad.

00:10:53.960 --> 00:10:56.120
There's something in my car I forgot to get.

00:10:56.120 --> 00:10:57.600
Feifei, don't even think about sneaking away.

00:10:58.320 --> 00:10:59.120
You promised me too.

00:10:59.120 --> 00:11:00.240
You'd listen to whatever I say.

00:11:00.480 --> 00:11:02.799
Our second treatment phase is about to begin.

00:11:06.360 --> 00:11:07.279
Hand over your phone.

00:11:08.159 --> 00:11:09.120
My phone?

00:11:09.960 --> 00:11:10.639
No, Uncle...

00:11:10.639 --> 00:11:12.240
I can't live without my phone, Uncle!

00:11:12.240 --> 00:11:13.159
What's that got to do with me?

00:11:13.159 --> 00:11:13.879
Hand it over.

00:11:19.919 --> 00:11:20.720
Good boy.

00:11:21.000 --> 00:11:22.759
Granny, sorry to trouble you.

00:11:24.639 --> 00:11:25.320
Hang in there.

00:11:32.960 --> 00:11:33.799
Hello, Granny.

00:11:44.240 --> 00:11:45.240
Don't worry.

00:11:46.080 --> 00:11:47.919
When my dad was Feifei's age...

00:11:47.919 --> 00:11:49.080
he was already sent down to the countryside.

00:11:49.279 --> 00:11:50.799
The conditions were even worse than this.

00:11:51.000 --> 00:11:52.240
He stayed there for over ten years.

00:11:52.240 --> 00:11:53.879
Kids of Feifei's generation...

00:11:53.879 --> 00:11:55.960
how can they compare to our parents' generation?

00:11:56.120 --> 00:11:57.360
They can't even compare...

00:11:57.360 --> 00:11:58.600
to our generation.

00:11:59.399 --> 00:12:01.919
Weren't you the one who always wanted Feifei to suffer a bit?

00:12:04.080 --> 00:12:05.200
No, I... that...

00:12:06.200 --> 00:12:07.080
But you...

00:12:08.000 --> 00:12:08.879
Back then, I...

00:12:08.879 --> 00:12:10.639
let Feifei spend money recklessly.

00:12:10.639 --> 00:12:11.759
Weren't you angry about that?

00:12:11.759 --> 00:12:12.799
Of course!

00:12:13.000 --> 00:12:14.679
Letting a kid spend money like that...

00:12:14.679 --> 00:12:16.120
anyone would be angry.

00:12:16.799 --> 00:12:17.799
Let me tell you something.

00:12:18.240 --> 00:12:19.440
Feifei, this kid...

00:12:19.440 --> 00:12:22.159
has lots of ideas, but he's young and inexperienced.

00:12:22.480 --> 00:12:24.000
I want him to...

00:12:24.000 --> 00:12:26.279
quickly experience this kind of extreme environment.

00:12:26.279 --> 00:12:27.639
To make him mature quickly.

00:12:28.320 --> 00:12:29.879
I believe with his intelligence...

00:12:30.080 --> 00:12:31.519
he'll figure it out soon enough.

00:12:33.279 --> 00:12:34.879
Let's just wait and see the results.

00:12:36.360 --> 00:12:37.480
It's not just that.

00:12:37.960 --> 00:12:39.120
There's also your part in this.

00:12:42.559 --> 00:12:43.320
Me?

00:12:48.879 --> 00:12:49.480
Bro.

00:12:49.679 --> 00:12:50.440
Qiu'er.

00:12:50.759 --> 00:12:52.879
Lianbao called and told me to come here.

00:12:52.879 --> 00:12:55.200
He was in a huge rush but wouldn't say why.

00:12:55.480 --> 00:12:57.480
Don't worry about it. You'll know when you get here.

00:12:57.480 --> 00:12:58.080
Have some water.

00:12:59.480 --> 00:13:00.159
It hurts.

00:13:00.399 --> 00:13:01.120
What's wrong?

00:13:01.480 --> 00:13:02.600
Just the usual aches.

00:13:02.600 --> 00:13:03.279
Big Brother.

00:13:04.200 --> 00:13:05.039
Qiu'er's here too.

00:13:05.039 --> 00:13:06.240
You got here fast.

00:13:06.919 --> 00:13:09.320
So, you said the money's settled?

00:13:09.320 --> 00:13:10.080
Yeah.

00:13:11.120 --> 00:13:12.320
Really?

00:13:12.759 --> 00:13:14.080
The money's settled?

00:13:16.600 --> 00:13:19.480
Look at that smug face. Must be a lot of money.

00:13:20.240 --> 00:13:22.399
Not bad. This might actually work out.

00:13:22.399 --> 00:13:23.320
Of course.

00:13:26.200 --> 00:13:28.039
What kind of money is this?

00:13:28.200 --> 00:13:29.679
Investor money.

00:13:30.159 --> 00:13:31.559
Weren't you always worried about me...

00:13:31.559 --> 00:13:32.720
...losing money on this?

00:13:33.039 --> 00:13:34.799
This time, there's no gamble.

00:13:34.960 --> 00:13:36.399
You don't need to worry about a thing.

00:13:37.720 --> 00:13:38.759
Who gave you the money?

00:13:40.279 --> 00:13:42.679
Don't you worry about that. I have my ways.

00:13:43.679 --> 00:13:44.759
Things have already come to this.

00:13:44.960 --> 00:13:46.120
I'm going all in.

00:13:46.559 --> 00:13:48.720
Let's go see Old Xie.

00:13:48.840 --> 00:13:49.960
Sworn brothers.

00:13:50.080 --> 00:13:51.600
This guy knows Martin.

00:13:51.600 --> 00:13:52.799
No mistake, Mr. Xie.

00:13:52.879 --> 00:13:53.679
Their proposal...

00:13:53.679 --> 00:13:55.559
...was done by Director Dong's team at Xinxin.

00:13:55.559 --> 00:13:57.240
I've already asked around at Xinxin.

00:13:57.840 --> 00:13:59.679
Everyone, sorry, sorry.

00:13:59.679 --> 00:14:00.559
I'm late, I'm late.

00:14:00.559 --> 00:14:01.240
Come on, come on.

00:14:02.159 --> 00:14:02.919
Lianbao.

00:14:03.000 --> 00:14:04.080
I didn't expect our little matter...

00:14:04.080 --> 00:14:05.200
...to go so smoothly.

00:14:05.200 --> 00:14:06.080
Of course.

00:14:06.080 --> 00:14:09.240
Alright. I didn't befriend you for nothing.

00:14:10.480 --> 00:14:11.960
As long as Mr. Ma is in this project...

00:14:11.960 --> 00:14:13.080
...everything's fine.

00:14:13.960 --> 00:14:16.840
Don't worry, all four of us brothers are in.

00:14:17.080 --> 00:14:17.840
Deal.

00:14:18.320 --> 00:14:19.200
We'll see you later then.

00:14:19.200 --> 00:14:19.759
Okay.

00:14:21.000 --> 00:14:22.120
Hold on, Second Brother.

00:14:23.320 --> 00:14:25.279
I never said before...

00:14:25.279 --> 00:14:27.120
...that I'd work for you just because you have money.

00:14:27.759 --> 00:14:29.279
What are you talking about?

00:14:29.559 --> 00:14:31.679
I'm the one following *you*.

00:14:32.960 --> 00:14:34.080
Besides...

00:14:34.279 --> 00:14:35.679
...it's not just the two of us.

00:14:35.799 --> 00:14:37.080
Qiu'er's here too, right?

00:14:37.759 --> 00:14:39.159
I also promised...

00:14:39.639 --> 00:14:41.240
...him five percent of the shares.

00:14:42.759 --> 00:14:44.399
Look how tough things are for Qiu'er right now.

00:14:44.559 --> 00:14:46.279
Shouldn't we think about helping him out?

00:14:46.279 --> 00:14:48.080
Yeah, my situation right now is really...

00:14:48.080 --> 00:14:48.919
...indescribable.

00:14:48.919 --> 00:14:50.919
I've been pushed all the way to the Arctic Circle.

00:14:51.200 --> 00:14:52.279
Who knows how long...

00:14:52.279 --> 00:14:53.559
...I'll have to hold on like this.

00:14:53.679 --> 00:14:55.840
I don't even dare tell my parents or my wife.

00:14:55.840 --> 00:14:57.679
So I really have to rely on you two.

00:14:57.679 --> 00:15:00.240
Hey, let's not play the pity card, okay?

00:15:00.240 --> 00:15:02.519
I'm not playing a card, I'm just telling the truth, Bro.

00:15:03.440 --> 00:15:06.320
Look, we need to talk about this properly.

00:15:06.759 --> 00:15:08.639
Big Brother, let me say a couple more things.

00:15:08.639 --> 00:15:10.759
No, can *you* listen to me for a second?

00:15:10.759 --> 00:15:12.120
Let me say something first.

00:15:12.840 --> 00:15:14.879
I'm not doing this for anything else...

00:15:15.399 --> 00:15:17.320
...I'm just doing it for our Yuanyuan.

00:15:17.799 --> 00:15:18.720
Look.

00:15:19.240 --> 00:15:19.919
This Lao Kai...

00:15:19.919 --> 00:15:21.600
...is always giving her this and that.

00:15:21.960 --> 00:15:23.240
I can't do anything for her.

00:15:23.639 --> 00:15:24.879
Don't you think in Yuanyuan's heart...

00:15:25.120 --> 00:15:26.480
...she won't treat us differently?

00:15:28.039 --> 00:15:29.440
But I have to let her know...

00:15:30.120 --> 00:15:31.279
...what others can give...

00:15:31.440 --> 00:15:32.759
...her real father can give too.

00:15:32.759 --> 00:15:35.799
No, no, the kid wouldn't think like that.

00:15:35.799 --> 00:15:37.519
No, Big Brother, listen to me.

00:15:37.519 --> 00:15:39.639
Stop! Can you all listen to *me*?

00:15:39.639 --> 00:15:40.519
Fine, you talk.

00:15:42.600 --> 00:15:44.279
The moment you two walked in just now...

00:15:44.759 --> 00:15:45.879
...I wanted to say...

00:15:46.440 --> 00:15:51.399
...let's do this together, us brothers.

00:15:52.559 --> 00:15:53.240
Well...

00:15:54.600 --> 00:15:56.279
Bro, you should've said that earlier!

00:15:56.279 --> 00:15:57.480
You had me all worked up and rushing around.

00:15:57.480 --> 00:15:59.200
I was even trying to persuade you to join in.

00:15:59.200 --> 00:15:59.600
Seriously.

00:15:59.600 --> 00:16:00.360
Exactly.

00:16:00.360 --> 00:16:03.600
But... I have one condition.

00:16:03.840 --> 00:16:05.840
Even if you had a hundred, a thousand, ten thousand...

00:16:05.840 --> 00:16:06.759
...I'd agree to them all.

00:16:06.759 --> 00:16:07.399
Don't...

00:16:08.360 --> 00:16:09.279
Just one condition.

00:16:09.279 --> 00:16:09.960
Go on.

00:16:10.679 --> 00:16:12.240
The condition is...

00:16:12.240 --> 00:16:16.639
...Weiguo works with the three of us.

00:16:21.320 --> 00:16:22.320
Hold on, Big Brother.

00:16:22.720 --> 00:16:24.480
Why is he involved in this?

00:16:24.600 --> 00:16:26.120
Do you remember your old nickname?

00:16:26.120 --> 00:16:27.120
"The Baofang Protector."

00:16:27.600 --> 00:16:29.159
Do you still deserve that title now?

00:16:29.480 --> 00:16:31.159
That was all when we were kids.

00:16:31.159 --> 00:16:32.600
Why bring that up?

00:16:34.519 --> 00:16:35.759
Feifei told me...

00:16:36.120 --> 00:16:37.919
...that you two used to be really close.

00:16:38.080 --> 00:16:39.360
He'd tell you everything.

00:16:39.600 --> 00:16:41.120
And he really looked up to you.

00:16:41.759 --> 00:16:43.080
But at some point...

00:16:43.080 --> 00:16:44.559
...you two had nothing to say to each other.

00:16:44.720 --> 00:16:46.120
And you didn't understand each other anymore.

00:16:47.159 --> 00:16:48.159
I guess...

00:16:48.480 --> 00:16:50.440
...it's because that idol dad disappeared.

00:16:50.559 --> 00:16:52.840
Hey, wait, why am I getting dragged into this?

00:16:53.320 --> 00:16:54.200
I want to ask you...

00:16:54.879 --> 00:16:56.960
...what have you been doing all these years?

00:16:57.759 --> 00:17:00.399
I just take care of the shop...

00:17:00.759 --> 00:17:02.000
...take care of things at home...

00:17:02.000 --> 00:17:04.079
...supervise Feifei's studies...

00:17:04.160 --> 00:17:06.039
...manage his life and all that.

00:17:06.680 --> 00:17:07.400
Really?

00:17:08.240 --> 00:17:10.599
I see you playing with cars, playing with sneakers...

00:17:10.599 --> 00:17:12.359
...watching Douyin, watching livestreams...

00:17:12.839 --> 00:17:14.920
...and in your free time, you're with your old buddies...

00:17:14.920 --> 00:17:15.920
...jamming music together.

00:17:17.039 --> 00:17:18.559
That's not doing anything serious.

00:17:31.359 --> 00:17:32.960
Weiguo, come here.

00:17:41.200 --> 00:17:42.240
And at the shop...

00:17:42.240 --> 00:17:43.240
...it's all Sister-in-law, Xiao Gui...

00:17:43.240 --> 00:17:44.599
...and Xiao Li who are running things.

00:17:45.039 --> 00:17:46.279
And I also heard...

00:17:46.279 --> 00:17:47.400
...that for over a decade now...

00:17:47.559 --> 00:17:49.359
...you haven't roasted a single duck from start to finish.

00:17:49.480 --> 00:17:50.039
Am I right?

00:17:50.279 --> 00:17:53.119
No, the hardships I was meant to endure...

00:17:53.119 --> 00:17:55.160
I've already endured them all, right?

00:17:55.279 --> 00:17:56.839
The life I'm living now...

00:17:56.839 --> 00:17:59.480
This is the life of a winner, you know?

00:17:59.480 --> 00:18:00.519
A winner in life.

00:18:00.839 --> 00:18:01.799
And another thing...

00:18:02.200 --> 00:18:04.480
I just don't feel that right now...

00:18:04.480 --> 00:18:07.720
There's any so-called serious business worth my doing.

00:18:09.759 --> 00:18:11.640
Hasn't Li Lianbao been trying to rope you in...

00:18:11.640 --> 00:18:14.079
To start a business with Peng Le Xuan?

00:18:14.680 --> 00:18:17.599
I think it's a great opportunity.

00:18:19.559 --> 00:18:20.720
Come on, sit here.

00:18:26.400 --> 00:18:27.519
I have conditions too.

00:18:27.519 --> 00:18:29.160
What gives you the right to set conditions?

00:18:29.279 --> 00:18:30.519
Big Brother agreed!

00:18:38.200 --> 00:18:40.039
Then I have to say this upfront.

00:18:40.680 --> 00:18:42.480
If it's about me apologizing to you again...

00:18:42.480 --> 00:18:43.480
I absolutely refuse.

00:18:44.240 --> 00:18:45.720
You want to apologize to me?

00:18:45.799 --> 00:18:47.200
It won't be that easy.

00:18:47.319 --> 00:18:48.839
Unless you're sincerely convinced...

00:18:48.839 --> 00:18:49.839
Otherwise, I won't accept it.

00:18:49.839 --> 00:18:50.319
Alright, alright.

00:18:50.319 --> 00:18:51.559
Keep dreaming your foolish dreams.

00:18:51.559 --> 00:18:52.720
Even if you begged on your knees, that day will never come.

00:18:52.720 --> 00:18:53.799
Enough, enough, enough.

00:18:53.799 --> 00:18:54.920
Alright, Brother, alright, alright.

00:18:54.920 --> 00:18:57.039
Hey, hey, you two, stop fighting the moment you meet.

00:18:57.039 --> 00:18:59.559
Let's, let's talk business first, okay?

00:18:59.559 --> 00:19:01.480
What conditions? Tell us.

00:19:02.759 --> 00:19:05.039
I want one percent of Peng Le Xuan's shares.

00:19:05.039 --> 00:19:06.640
And the operational management of Peng Le Xuan.

00:19:06.759 --> 00:19:09.039
Along with a one-vote veto power.

00:19:09.039 --> 00:19:09.880
On what grounds?

00:19:09.880 --> 00:19:11.559
On the grounds that Big Brother agreed! That's what!

00:19:13.400 --> 00:19:14.440
Look, here's the thing.

00:19:15.000 --> 00:19:16.000
The four of us brothers...

00:19:17.039 --> 00:19:18.519
For Peng Le Xuan...

00:19:18.920 --> 00:19:19.960
Coming together...

00:19:21.079 --> 00:19:22.359
How wonderful is that?

00:19:23.119 --> 00:19:23.920
Come on, come on.

00:19:23.920 --> 00:19:24.759
I think so too.

00:19:24.759 --> 00:19:25.960
Let's use tea instead of wine.

00:19:26.279 --> 00:19:27.039
Bottoms up.

00:19:27.440 --> 00:19:28.480
Come on, come on.

00:19:28.480 --> 00:19:29.920
I think I can accept it, really.

00:19:29.920 --> 00:19:30.519
Second Brother.

00:19:31.200 --> 00:19:31.720
Come on.

00:19:31.880 --> 00:19:32.440
Hurry up.

00:19:32.440 --> 00:19:33.559
Hurry, hurry, Brother.

00:19:37.400 --> 00:19:38.839
Big Brother agreed too.

00:19:39.400 --> 00:19:40.920
Just do it for Peng Le Xuan.

00:19:41.519 --> 00:19:42.680
Come on, cheers.

00:19:42.680 --> 00:19:44.400
Bottoms up, four brothers.

00:19:44.400 --> 00:19:45.160
Four brothers.

00:19:45.160 --> 00:19:46.000
Brothers.

00:20:27.640 --> 00:20:28.599
Everyone.

00:20:28.759 --> 00:20:31.000
Later, eat as heartily as you can.

00:20:31.000 --> 00:20:32.559
If there's no room inside...

00:20:32.559 --> 00:20:34.079
Everyone waits outside for a table.

00:20:37.880 --> 00:20:39.839
Hey, did you all hear me or not?

00:20:40.279 --> 00:20:41.759
We hired you as extras.

00:20:41.759 --> 00:20:43.720
Extras are actors too.

00:20:44.039 --> 00:20:46.240
You have to do justice to this job.

00:20:46.799 --> 00:20:48.480
If anyone messes up their performance later...

00:20:48.480 --> 00:20:49.799
Don't blame me for not paying you.

00:20:50.480 --> 00:20:51.880
Uncle Tong, Uncle Tong, here, here.

00:20:51.880 --> 00:20:52.880
This table is reserved for you.

00:20:52.880 --> 00:20:54.799
Yes, yes, quick, quick, please sit here.

00:20:55.799 --> 00:20:56.480
Not bad.

00:20:56.480 --> 00:20:57.440
Lively, huh?

00:20:57.559 --> 00:20:58.839
Yangzi, this table, this table.

00:20:58.839 --> 00:20:59.759
Okay, okay, okay.

00:21:00.279 --> 00:21:02.400
Well, thank you all for your support.

00:21:02.400 --> 00:21:03.079
Old Wang said...

00:21:03.079 --> 00:21:04.240
Today's meal is on him.

00:21:04.240 --> 00:21:05.480
Great! Okay, okay.

00:21:05.720 --> 00:21:06.400
I say...

00:21:06.400 --> 00:21:08.720
Our alley hasn't been this lively in a long time.

00:21:08.720 --> 00:21:09.759
Isn't that the truth?

00:21:23.000 --> 00:21:24.279
President Wang, President Wang.

00:21:26.680 --> 00:21:27.640
Come on, Qiu'er, get up.

00:21:27.640 --> 00:21:28.759
Old Wang.

00:21:28.759 --> 00:21:30.839
The big show is about to begin, right?

00:21:31.000 --> 00:21:32.079
That's why they say...

00:21:32.079 --> 00:21:33.920
Fortune shifts like the river's flow.

00:21:33.920 --> 00:21:35.400
You brothers are really...

00:21:35.400 --> 00:21:36.680
About to turn things around this time.

00:21:36.680 --> 00:21:38.000
What 'Old Wang'?

00:21:38.000 --> 00:21:40.200
He's President Wang now, call him President Wang.

00:21:40.640 --> 00:21:41.119
Thank you.

00:21:41.119 --> 00:21:42.200
President Wang.

00:21:42.359 --> 00:21:43.480
I say, President Wang...

00:21:43.640 --> 00:21:46.079
With your multi-million dollar business...

00:21:46.079 --> 00:21:46.839
When I come back in the future...

00:21:46.839 --> 00:21:48.079
Will it be free of charge?

00:21:48.079 --> 00:21:49.880
From now on, when you come, there's a minimum spend.

00:21:50.079 --> 00:21:50.839
Starting at three hundred yuan.

00:21:50.839 --> 00:21:51.960
Otherwise, don't even come in.

00:21:53.079 --> 00:21:54.200
That won't do.

00:21:54.200 --> 00:21:56.119
It should be at least eight hundred.

00:21:57.960 --> 00:22:00.319
In the future, if you haven't won five million...

00:22:00.319 --> 00:22:02.480
You won't even be allowed through Peng Le Xuan's door.

00:22:02.480 --> 00:22:03.519
Listen up, everyone.

00:22:03.519 --> 00:22:04.519
Later, be quick about it.

00:22:04.519 --> 00:22:06.160
Come to my place to win five million!

00:22:34.799 --> 00:22:35.519
Coming, coming!

00:22:35.519 --> 00:22:36.119
Coming!

00:22:36.119 --> 00:22:36.759
Coming, coming!

00:22:36.759 --> 00:22:38.240
Let's be lively, everyone!

00:22:39.039 --> 00:22:40.599
More enthusiasm, more enthusiasm!

00:22:40.599 --> 00:22:41.680
Let's eat, let's eat!

00:22:42.759 --> 00:22:43.799
They're all waiting for a table.

00:22:44.039 --> 00:22:44.799
It's so popular.

00:22:44.799 --> 00:22:45.559
Yeah.

00:22:47.680 --> 00:22:49.559
The taste is pretty good, right?

00:22:49.799 --> 00:22:50.880
Authentic, authentic, authentic!

00:22:50.880 --> 00:22:52.759
Sister-in-law, let me introduce you.

00:22:52.759 --> 00:22:53.279
Hello.

00:22:53.279 --> 00:22:54.960
This is Mr. Xie, who's planning to invest in our Peng Le Xuan.

00:22:54.960 --> 00:22:55.920
This is Mr. Xie.

00:22:55.920 --> 00:22:57.279
Hello, hello! Welcome!

00:22:57.279 --> 00:22:59.400
I'm telling you, the roast duck at Peng Le Xuan...

00:22:59.400 --> 00:23:01.680
...this flavor has been the same for decades. Truly authentic.

00:23:01.680 --> 00:23:03.839
Yeah, if I don't eat it for two days, I start craving it.

00:23:03.880 --> 00:23:05.079
I'd even want to live here.

00:23:05.079 --> 00:23:06.079
Eat it for every meal.

00:23:06.200 --> 00:23:08.000
Old Xie, take a look.

00:23:08.000 --> 00:23:09.799
Our place here, although not very big...

00:23:09.799 --> 00:23:11.079
...is really bustling with customers.

00:23:11.079 --> 00:23:11.799
You saw it at the entrance.

00:23:11.799 --> 00:23:12.880
It's all people waiting for tables.

00:23:13.000 --> 00:23:13.680
Not bad.

00:23:14.400 --> 00:23:15.480
Judging by this...

00:23:15.480 --> 00:23:17.319
...the annual turnover must be substantial.

00:23:17.599 --> 00:23:18.640
This business is profitable.

00:23:18.640 --> 00:23:19.359
Right?

00:23:19.359 --> 00:23:20.440
Come on, let's talk upstairs.

00:23:20.440 --> 00:23:20.920
Alright.

00:23:20.920 --> 00:23:21.880
Yes, please go upstairs.

00:23:22.319 --> 00:23:24.119
You two, enjoy your meal, take your time.

00:23:27.559 --> 00:23:29.559
Old Xie, quick, quick, inside.

00:23:30.799 --> 00:23:31.680
Really great.

00:23:31.680 --> 00:23:33.640
You're the guest of honor today. Sit here.

00:23:34.119 --> 00:23:34.839
Sit, sit, sit.

00:23:34.839 --> 00:23:35.400
Come on, sit, sit, sit.

00:23:35.400 --> 00:23:35.839
Okay.

00:23:36.160 --> 00:23:37.000
Thank you.

00:23:37.480 --> 00:23:38.720
Have some tea.

00:23:40.319 --> 00:23:43.640
I'm Tong Qiu, also a shareholder of Peng Le Xuan.

00:23:44.200 --> 00:23:45.240
Just looking at your face...

00:23:45.240 --> 00:23:46.559
...you're a premium customer.

00:23:47.039 --> 00:23:47.799
Here's the thing.

00:23:47.920 --> 00:23:49.000
Our bank has a...

00:23:49.000 --> 00:23:50.759
...consumer loan with a limit of five hundred thousand.

00:23:50.759 --> 00:23:52.519
The annual interest rate is only three point one percent.

00:23:53.839 --> 00:23:54.799
What are you talking about?

00:23:55.400 --> 00:23:57.240
Wrong topic, sorry about that.

00:23:57.880 --> 00:23:59.000
You're something else.

00:23:59.400 --> 00:24:02.000
Old Xie, regarding Peng Le Xuan's situation...

00:24:02.000 --> 00:24:03.160
...you have a general understanding now.

00:24:03.400 --> 00:24:05.039
So, regarding our future cooperation...

00:24:05.039 --> 00:24:06.359
...do you see any other issues?

00:24:08.640 --> 00:24:11.680
Why isn't Ma Weiguo here?

00:24:13.400 --> 00:24:17.000
He... he had a sudden emergency.

00:24:17.119 --> 00:24:18.119
He's been notified.

00:24:18.119 --> 00:24:19.079
He'll be here soon.

00:24:19.519 --> 00:24:21.119
The roast duck will be served right away.

00:24:21.119 --> 00:24:22.599
Let's talk while we eat.

00:24:24.359 --> 00:24:24.839
Alright.

00:24:25.599 --> 00:24:27.359
From last year to the first half of this year...

00:24:27.359 --> 00:24:28.519
...this boss surnamed Xie...

00:24:28.519 --> 00:24:30.759
...has expressed interest in cooperating with us several times.

00:24:30.759 --> 00:24:32.200
But it was always halted.

00:24:32.200 --> 00:24:33.119
We found that...

00:24:33.119 --> 00:24:34.720
...his company's core technology...

00:24:34.720 --> 00:24:35.960
...has patent disputes.

00:24:35.960 --> 00:24:38.480
There have been multiple court lawsuits in the past three months...

00:24:38.480 --> 00:24:40.960
...and records of debt evasion at multiple banks.

00:24:41.319 --> 00:24:42.519
Okay, thank you.

00:25:08.359 --> 00:25:09.279
How is it?

00:25:13.240 --> 00:25:14.039
Delicious.

00:25:15.400 --> 00:25:16.440
Of course.

00:25:16.440 --> 00:25:17.359
Let me tell you...

00:25:17.359 --> 00:25:19.119
Don't look down on my small shop...

00:25:19.119 --> 00:25:20.640
...but when it comes to roast duck...

00:25:20.839 --> 00:25:22.039
...in all of Beijing...

00:25:22.039 --> 00:25:23.160
...I've never acknowledged anyone as better.

00:25:23.160 --> 00:25:23.720
Yes.

00:25:25.319 --> 00:25:27.680
Just the way Brother Wang wheeled the duck in earlier...

00:25:27.839 --> 00:25:28.559
...was so refined.

00:25:28.920 --> 00:25:30.680
Truly worthy of a century-old establishment.

00:25:30.920 --> 00:25:33.160
And that technique for slicing the duck...

00:25:33.160 --> 00:25:34.839
...is absolutely a unique skill.

00:25:34.839 --> 00:25:36.240
You have a good eye, you have a good eye.

00:25:36.240 --> 00:25:37.400
Come on, come on, let me toast you.

00:25:37.400 --> 00:25:38.079
Come on, come on.

00:25:38.079 --> 00:25:38.920
Brother Wang, I toast you, I toast you.

00:25:38.920 --> 00:25:39.759
Come on, come on, Mr. Xie, here.

00:25:39.759 --> 00:25:40.839
Pleased to meet you, pleased to meet you.

00:25:40.839 --> 00:25:41.480
To you.

00:25:41.480 --> 00:25:42.160
To you.

00:25:42.160 --> 00:25:44.319
So, about this due diligence...

00:25:44.319 --> 00:25:45.160
...let's talk about it later.

00:25:45.160 --> 00:25:45.799
Good.

00:25:50.839 --> 00:25:54.640
Peng Le Xuan, and Brother Wang's capabilities...

00:25:54.920 --> 00:25:57.599
...I've already researched thoroughly.

00:25:59.079 --> 00:26:00.240
To be honest...

00:26:00.440 --> 00:26:01.839
...the main reason I came today...

00:26:01.839 --> 00:26:06.240
...was mainly to meet this Ma Weiguo.

00:26:06.880 --> 00:26:08.079
Hold on, Old Xie...

00:26:08.079 --> 00:26:08.960
...with all this talk...

00:26:08.960 --> 00:26:10.079
...you still don't trust me?

00:26:10.079 --> 00:26:11.000
That's not it.

00:26:11.359 --> 00:26:13.839
Lianbao, we've been friends for over ten years.

00:26:13.839 --> 00:26:15.000
For you to say that...

00:26:16.079 --> 00:26:17.200
On the other hand...

00:26:17.920 --> 00:26:19.640
All these years...

00:26:19.960 --> 00:26:21.440
...how come I've never heard you...

00:26:21.440 --> 00:26:22.680
...mention anything about Ma Weiguo?

00:26:23.119 --> 00:26:24.079
Confess honestly.

00:26:24.599 --> 00:26:27.319
Fine, I must produce ironclad proof.

00:26:27.640 --> 00:26:29.839
Qiu'er, pull up that photo.

00:26:31.200 --> 00:26:32.039
What photo?

00:26:32.039 --> 00:26:32.519
Take a look.

00:26:32.519 --> 00:26:33.240
Qiu'er, Qiu'er, Qiu'er!

00:26:33.240 --> 00:26:34.680
You come, come here and show Mr. Xie.

00:26:34.680 --> 00:26:35.640
You, you sit here.

00:26:35.640 --> 00:26:36.559
You sit here, you sit here.

00:26:36.559 --> 00:26:37.440
You show Mr. Xie.

00:26:37.440 --> 00:26:38.000
Alright.

00:26:38.000 --> 00:26:39.720
Qiu'er, come over here, come on, sit.

00:26:41.079 --> 00:26:42.200
Look at this.

00:26:43.200 --> 00:26:45.440
This is my Big Brother.

00:26:55.359 --> 00:26:56.160
It's especially delicious.

00:26:56.160 --> 00:26:58.079
It's the best on our street.

00:27:03.000 --> 00:27:03.559
Come on, come on.

00:27:03.559 --> 00:27:04.400
Bottoms up, bottoms up, bottoms up.

00:27:04.400 --> 00:27:06.200
Weiguo, sit here and eat.

00:27:06.200 --> 00:27:08.039
Sis, it wasn't me. Who called them over?

00:27:08.039 --> 00:27:09.480
Second Brother found them.

00:27:09.720 --> 00:27:11.039
They haven't even paid yet.

00:27:11.039 --> 00:27:11.920
Weiguo!

00:27:11.920 --> 00:27:13.559
Here to inspect again?

00:27:13.559 --> 00:27:14.240
See that?

00:27:14.240 --> 00:27:15.279
They're all upstairs.

00:27:15.279 --> 00:27:16.720
Discussing a multi-million dollar deal.

00:27:16.720 --> 00:27:18.000
Why aren't you going up?

00:27:18.240 --> 00:27:21.400
Alright, stop acting. Who hired you?

00:27:21.400 --> 00:27:22.640
Come to me for payment. Get out, now.

00:27:22.640 --> 00:27:23.319
What's the big idea?

00:27:23.319 --> 00:27:25.480
Stop acting. It's too fake.

00:27:25.480 --> 00:27:27.640
This is a multi-million dollar deal.

00:27:27.640 --> 00:27:29.119
You can't hire extras for this.

00:27:29.119 --> 00:27:30.039
Mr. Ma, sorry about that.

00:27:30.200 --> 00:27:31.039
I'll handle it.

00:27:31.160 --> 00:27:32.279
Lianbao found them, right?

00:27:32.480 --> 00:27:33.799
Get them out of here, quick.

00:27:34.640 --> 00:27:35.319
Come on, come on.

00:27:35.319 --> 00:27:36.079
Wrap it up, wrap it up.

00:27:36.079 --> 00:27:37.240
Come with me outside.

00:27:37.240 --> 00:27:38.160
Payment's outside.

00:27:38.160 --> 00:27:39.480
Come on, let's go, go.

00:27:39.480 --> 00:27:41.359
So fake. I'm going up first.

00:27:44.519 --> 00:27:45.079
Wait.

00:27:45.079 --> 00:27:45.720
Hold on.

00:27:47.000 --> 00:27:48.279
Is that it?

00:27:48.680 --> 00:27:50.599
I was just getting into the groove of eating.

00:27:50.720 --> 00:27:51.680
But you know what?

00:27:51.680 --> 00:27:52.920
No "buts."

00:27:53.039 --> 00:27:54.480
He's right in the courtyard next door.

00:27:54.480 --> 00:27:55.240
He'll be here any second.

00:27:55.240 --> 00:27:56.640
He's in the yard right next to us.

00:27:56.640 --> 00:27:57.880
He's literally next door.

00:27:59.000 --> 00:28:00.519
Why didn't you say so earlier?

00:28:01.720 --> 00:28:06.359
Alright then. I value Peng Le Xuan at thirty million.

00:28:06.920 --> 00:28:08.680
I'll invest three million first.

00:28:11.039 --> 00:28:11.720
Deal?

00:28:16.119 --> 00:28:16.880
A toast, a toast.

00:28:16.880 --> 00:28:17.880
Come on, come on.

00:28:17.880 --> 00:28:19.079
Wait, wait, wait.

00:28:19.759 --> 00:28:21.799
Quick, invite Mr. Ma over.

00:28:22.400 --> 00:28:23.079
Hurry up.

00:28:24.240 --> 00:28:26.319
Mr. Ma, it really is you.

00:28:26.319 --> 00:28:27.680
Here, take the seat of honor.

00:28:27.680 --> 00:28:28.079
Please.

00:28:28.079 --> 00:28:28.720
Let's sit and talk.

00:28:28.839 --> 00:28:29.400
After you.

00:28:32.000 --> 00:28:32.640
Alright, alright.

00:28:32.759 --> 00:28:33.920
Why are you sitting in my seat?

00:28:34.400 --> 00:28:35.000
Mr. Ma.

00:28:35.119 --> 00:28:36.359
Those extras of yours...

00:28:36.359 --> 00:28:37.440
I kicked them out.

00:28:37.839 --> 00:28:38.599
What do you mean?

00:28:38.599 --> 00:28:39.599
What do *you* mean?

00:28:39.599 --> 00:28:40.519
Too fake.

00:28:43.920 --> 00:28:44.680
Mr. Ma.

00:28:45.039 --> 00:28:46.559
Let me introduce myself.

00:28:46.680 --> 00:28:48.400
My surname is Xie, as in "thank you."

00:28:48.400 --> 00:28:48.920
Pleasure, pleasure, pleasure.

00:28:48.920 --> 00:28:49.440
Pleasure.

00:28:49.640 --> 00:28:52.039
Mr. Xie has already agreed to invest in us.

00:28:52.519 --> 00:28:54.000
To be able to work with you, Mr. Ma...

00:28:54.000 --> 00:28:56.279
...is a once-in-a-lifetime opportunity.

00:28:56.400 --> 00:28:58.160
We have to thank my buddy, Manager Li.

00:28:58.160 --> 00:28:59.279
For making the connection.

00:29:00.920 --> 00:29:01.640
Mr. Xie.

00:29:01.920 --> 00:29:03.680
What do you think of Peng Le Xuan's food?

00:29:03.680 --> 00:29:04.559
How is it?

00:29:04.720 --> 00:29:05.799
Extremely satisfied.

00:29:06.519 --> 00:29:09.079
Brother Wang truly lives up to his family's secret recipe.

00:29:10.200 --> 00:29:11.359
To be honest with you, Mr. Ma...

00:29:11.720 --> 00:29:12.839
...I've eaten at roast duck restaurants in Beijing...

00:29:12.839 --> 00:29:14.880
...if not a hundred, then at least several dozen.

00:29:15.279 --> 00:29:17.440
Brother Wang is definitely not inferior to any of them.

00:29:17.680 --> 00:29:18.680
As I said earlier...

00:29:18.799 --> 00:29:21.000
...I value Peng Le Xuan at thirty million.

00:29:21.279 --> 00:29:22.400
We'll sign the contract tomorrow.

00:29:23.200 --> 00:29:26.200
Mr. Ma, I must propose a toast to you.

00:29:27.079 --> 00:29:28.160
Today, I...

00:29:29.079 --> 00:29:30.720
...am truly honored to meet you.

00:29:31.279 --> 00:29:34.039
I've long heard of your great reputation.

00:29:34.480 --> 00:29:35.720
From now on...

00:29:36.039 --> 00:29:38.000
...we'll be like family.

00:29:38.880 --> 00:29:41.519
Mr. Ma, I toast to you.

00:29:42.000 --> 00:29:42.960
With you here...

00:29:42.960 --> 00:29:45.319
...I believe we can definitely carve out...

00:29:45.319 --> 00:29:46.680
...a vast territory.

00:29:46.680 --> 00:29:47.480
Bottoms up.

00:29:47.799 --> 00:29:48.960
Sorry, I don't drink.

00:29:49.359 --> 00:29:50.279
No problem.

00:29:53.240 --> 00:29:54.079
Peng Le Xuan...

00:29:54.079 --> 00:29:55.640
...was passed down from my ancestors.

00:29:55.759 --> 00:29:58.440
First my grandfather, then passed to him.

00:29:58.680 --> 00:29:59.720
He's my older cousin.

00:30:04.920 --> 00:30:05.640
I see.

00:30:07.000 --> 00:30:08.440
In that case, Mr. Ma...

00:30:09.039 --> 00:30:10.599
...I value it at fifty million.

00:30:11.680 --> 00:30:13.240
I'll take ten percent.

00:30:14.000 --> 00:30:15.599
Cash, paid in full upfront.

00:30:15.920 --> 00:30:19.480
No buyback clause. What do you say?

00:30:19.880 --> 00:30:22.960
Mr. Xie, for our Peng Le Xuan, really...

00:30:22.960 --> 00:30:24.880
...I'm at a loss for words.

00:30:27.960 --> 00:30:28.759
Eighty million.

00:30:47.559 --> 00:30:48.079
Deal.

00:30:48.240 --> 00:30:51.440
Mr. Ma, it's happily decided then.

00:30:51.599 --> 00:30:52.200
Mr. Ma.

00:30:53.000 --> 00:30:53.799
I'm sorry.

00:30:54.680 --> 00:30:55.880
I don't want to raise capital anymore.

00:30:56.880 --> 00:30:57.559
How about this...

00:30:58.079 --> 00:30:59.480
If there's a chance next time...

00:30:59.480 --> 00:31:00.720
...we can cooperate then, okay?

00:31:02.839 --> 00:31:03.359
It's not that I...

00:31:03.359 --> 00:31:03.759
Don't be like that.

00:31:03.759 --> 00:31:04.160
I...

00:31:07.359 --> 00:31:09.920
Maybe you should reconsider.

00:31:10.079 --> 00:31:10.880
Actually...

00:31:10.880 --> 00:31:12.319
...we could cooperate in many areas.

00:31:12.319 --> 00:31:13.920
I said, next time.

00:31:14.759 --> 00:31:15.759
It's hopeless.

00:31:15.759 --> 00:31:16.440
He's coming.

00:31:16.440 --> 00:31:17.960
He's here, quick, quick.

00:31:18.920 --> 00:31:20.920
You know, this Peng Le Xuan is an old, established brand.

00:31:20.920 --> 00:31:22.039
I've been eating their roast duck for decades.

00:31:22.039 --> 00:31:23.200
Uncle Tong, Uncle Tong, stop talking.

00:31:23.200 --> 00:31:23.799
What's wrong?

00:31:23.799 --> 00:31:25.400
If I don't eat it for two days, I crave it.

00:31:25.880 --> 00:31:27.599
These two are still acting here.

00:31:29.079 --> 00:31:31.000
Don't try to fool an old hand.

00:31:31.799 --> 00:31:32.799
Who are you performing for?

00:31:33.240 --> 00:31:34.960
This is purely to liven up the atmosphere.

00:31:35.960 --> 00:31:36.799
What are you trying to do?

00:31:37.039 --> 00:31:38.480
Uncle, you two went a bit overboard.

00:31:38.480 --> 00:31:41.000
There's no one left, and you're doing it again?

00:31:41.119 --> 00:31:42.640
I came here with sincerity.

00:31:42.759 --> 00:31:44.000
This Mr. Ma is totally unreasonable.

00:31:44.000 --> 00:31:44.880
That's just his temper.

00:31:44.880 --> 00:31:46.160
I'll talk to him properly later.

00:31:46.160 --> 00:31:47.000
He's impressive, sure.

00:31:47.000 --> 00:31:47.799
But he's not so impressive...

00:31:47.799 --> 00:31:49.039
...that the Earth stops turning without him.

00:31:49.039 --> 00:31:49.400
Yes, yes, yes.

00:31:49.400 --> 00:31:50.920
Putting on airs. Let's go.

00:31:52.599 --> 00:31:53.359
Old Xie.

00:32:00.319 --> 00:32:01.720
What is this all about?

00:32:08.799 --> 00:32:11.000
Ma Weiguo, are you insane?

00:32:11.240 --> 00:32:12.240
You don't want fifty million?

00:32:12.240 --> 00:32:13.279
You don't want eighty million either?

00:32:13.279 --> 00:32:14.440
And you even drove the guy away!

00:32:14.440 --> 00:32:15.000
Alright, alright.

00:32:15.000 --> 00:32:16.599
So that's why you've been sticking around.

00:32:16.599 --> 00:32:17.880
Insisting on joining us.

00:32:17.880 --> 00:32:19.200
What's your scheme? Spit it out.

00:32:19.200 --> 00:32:20.240
Sit down, sit down, sit down.

00:32:20.240 --> 00:32:20.960
But seriously.

00:32:20.960 --> 00:32:21.759
This eighty million...

00:32:21.759 --> 00:32:23.319
Ten percent is eight million.

00:32:23.319 --> 00:32:25.319
That could buy a three-bedroom inside the Fourth Ring Road.

00:32:25.319 --> 00:32:26.720
You could even buy a villa out by the Sixth Ring.

00:32:26.799 --> 00:32:28.039
Weiguo, you...

00:32:28.279 --> 00:32:28.839
You...

00:32:28.960 --> 00:32:30.359
No, no, listen.

00:32:30.519 --> 00:32:32.119
Weiguo said that...

00:32:32.440 --> 00:32:34.240
I think he has his reasons.

00:32:34.240 --> 00:32:35.319
Let's not jump to conclusions.

00:32:35.599 --> 00:32:37.359
Weiguo, tell us what you're thinking.

00:32:37.480 --> 00:32:39.720
Hold on, Big Brother. I see it now.

00:32:40.119 --> 00:32:42.599
Ever since Ma Weiguo said he'd get Feifei into university,

00:32:42.720 --> 00:32:43.880
you've been covering for him.

00:32:44.039 --> 00:32:45.240
No matter what he says or does,

00:32:45.240 --> 00:32:46.200
he's always right.

00:32:47.200 --> 00:32:48.640
You'd better watch out.

00:32:48.640 --> 00:32:50.160
When he messes things up for Feifei,

00:32:50.160 --> 00:32:51.480
you'll be the one crying.

00:32:51.480 --> 00:32:53.279
No, look at what you're saying.

00:32:54.400 --> 00:32:55.960
I'm putting my foot down today.

00:32:56.799 --> 00:32:58.319
Weiguo is the one I brought in

00:32:58.319 --> 00:32:59.880
to work on Peng Le Xuan with us.

00:33:01.119 --> 00:33:02.960
All four of us, not one can be missing.

00:33:03.240 --> 00:33:05.640
Let's not create conflict among ourselves first.

00:33:05.640 --> 00:33:06.880
Let's first hear what Weiguo

00:33:06.880 --> 00:33:09.359
actually thinks, okay?

00:33:09.960 --> 00:33:11.720
Go on, what do you mean?

00:33:15.000 --> 00:33:15.880
I think it's like this.

00:33:16.000 --> 00:33:18.599
Let's not look for outside money.

00:33:19.319 --> 00:33:21.400
I'll invest in Peng Le Xuan myself.

00:33:21.400 --> 00:33:22.359
Great!

00:33:23.559 --> 00:33:25.000
So that eighty million just now...

00:33:25.000 --> 00:33:26.119
was just a smokescreen?

00:33:26.599 --> 00:33:28.480
Those investors aren't fools.

00:33:28.920 --> 00:33:30.519
He agreed to invest eighty million

00:33:30.519 --> 00:33:32.640
in Peng Le Xuan in just twenty seconds.

00:33:32.720 --> 00:33:35.400
That means Peng Le Xuan has great commercial potential.

00:33:35.880 --> 00:33:37.599
I don't know much about the restaurant business.

00:33:37.839 --> 00:33:38.680
So I used that guy

00:33:38.680 --> 00:33:39.759
as a test run, that's all.

00:33:39.759 --> 00:33:42.759
See? What did I tell you?

00:33:43.079 --> 00:33:44.599
The reason Weiguo could build

00:33:44.599 --> 00:33:46.160
such a big business in the US...

00:33:46.160 --> 00:33:47.519
Every single step...

00:33:47.519 --> 00:33:49.079
was carefully thought out.

00:33:49.079 --> 00:33:51.240
Strategizing, you understand?

00:33:51.559 --> 00:33:52.559
Go on.

00:33:52.559 --> 00:33:53.559
So now,

00:33:53.920 --> 00:33:55.720
let's properly discuss

00:33:56.359 --> 00:33:58.599
how to make Peng Le Xuan successful.

00:34:02.359 --> 00:34:07.359
Big Brother, the fundamental problem lies with you.

00:34:08.559 --> 00:34:09.559
Me? Me?

00:34:09.559 --> 00:34:10.639
I have a problem?

00:34:14.440 --> 00:34:15.880
If the problem is with me,

00:34:15.880 --> 00:34:17.599
I'll definitely change, okay?

00:34:17.599 --> 00:34:18.960
What's the problem?

00:34:19.039 --> 00:34:20.039
I'll be blunt.

00:34:20.599 --> 00:34:22.119
Your roast duck is subpar.

00:34:24.239 --> 00:34:26.159
Are you out of your mind?

00:34:26.599 --> 00:34:27.960
If you want to talk about other things,

00:34:27.960 --> 00:34:29.320
we can discuss them.

00:34:29.320 --> 00:34:31.519
But if you say my roast duck has problems,

00:34:31.519 --> 00:34:32.840
I won't stand for it.

00:34:33.360 --> 00:34:34.719
Lianbao, Qiu'er.

00:34:35.679 --> 00:34:37.119
You've eaten it for so many years.

00:34:37.440 --> 00:34:38.519
Haven't you noticed?

00:34:39.000 --> 00:34:40.239
The duck's flavor has changed.

00:34:41.239 --> 00:34:44.199
I... I don't think it's changed.

00:34:44.199 --> 00:34:45.079
It's the same.

00:34:45.679 --> 00:34:46.519
Big Brother,

00:34:46.960 --> 00:34:48.280
what did I tell you?

00:34:48.800 --> 00:34:50.280
This is nitpicking.

00:34:50.280 --> 00:34:51.480
Looking for trouble.

00:34:51.480 --> 00:34:52.320
Hold on, Weiguo.

00:34:53.119 --> 00:34:55.559
I was just defending you earlier.

00:34:56.239 --> 00:34:58.679
Let's not be like a pancake rolling a meatball...

00:34:58.679 --> 00:35:01.079
and then firing a cannon at it, okay?

00:35:04.559 --> 00:35:05.400
Fine, then.

00:35:05.679 --> 00:35:06.280
Big Brother.

00:35:06.280 --> 00:35:07.840
Let's hear other people's opinions.

00:35:12.199 --> 00:35:13.800
I don't believe it.

00:35:14.400 --> 00:35:16.320
I'll go roast two more ducks.

00:35:16.840 --> 00:35:18.320
We'll all taste them together.

00:35:21.360 --> 00:35:22.639
I want to see

00:35:22.639 --> 00:35:24.400
what he's really trying to pull.

00:35:28.679 --> 00:35:29.639
Big Brother,

00:35:29.760 --> 00:35:31.400
what did that riddle you just said mean?

00:35:31.400 --> 00:35:32.639
I didn't quite get it.

00:35:37.800 --> 00:35:38.920
Try it, try it.

00:35:40.559 --> 00:35:41.719
Try this palate cleanser.

00:35:56.400 --> 00:35:57.760
This flavor is so authentic.

00:35:57.760 --> 00:35:58.679
For decades,

00:35:58.679 --> 00:36:00.280
it's always been this taste. Remarkable.

00:36:00.280 --> 00:36:01.719
Truly worthy of being an old, established brand.

00:36:01.719 --> 00:36:03.360
The duck is sliced well too.

00:36:03.360 --> 00:36:04.519
Willow-leaf slices.

00:36:04.519 --> 00:36:05.679
Every cut has both skin and meat.

00:36:05.679 --> 00:36:06.920
No flaws, absolutely none.

00:36:06.920 --> 00:36:09.079
Our Lao Wang was extra serious today.

00:36:09.079 --> 00:36:11.679
He hasn't put in this much effort in years.

00:36:12.559 --> 00:36:14.639
Uncle Tong, Brother Dayang.

00:36:15.440 --> 00:36:17.480
I'd like to ask you the first question.

00:36:17.880 --> 00:36:19.440
Go ahead, go ahead.

00:36:19.599 --> 00:36:22.239
You've both eaten roast duck from other places.

00:36:22.400 --> 00:36:25.079
How do you think their taste compares

00:36:25.079 --> 00:36:25.960
to Big Brother's?

00:36:26.280 --> 00:36:26.880
Well...

00:36:28.639 --> 00:36:30.960
I went to Bianyifang the other day.

00:36:30.960 --> 00:36:31.679
And I thought to myself,

00:36:31.679 --> 00:36:32.639
their duck...

00:36:32.639 --> 00:36:34.519
isn't really any different from Lao Wang's.

00:36:34.519 --> 00:36:35.840
Why do they charge so much more?

00:36:35.840 --> 00:36:37.039
That's exactly the point.

00:36:37.039 --> 00:36:37.599
Right?

00:36:37.599 --> 00:36:39.480
I can't taste any difference at all.

00:36:39.480 --> 00:36:40.639
That *is* the problem.

00:36:41.519 --> 00:36:42.760
A century-old, established brand...

00:36:42.760 --> 00:36:43.679
having the exact same flavor

00:36:43.679 --> 00:36:44.719
as other roast duck shops...

00:36:44.880 --> 00:36:46.440
can that be called a century-old brand?

00:36:46.440 --> 00:36:47.719
Can it be called Peng Le Xuan?

00:36:48.039 --> 00:36:50.000
No, you're just picking a fight on purpose.

00:36:50.280 --> 00:36:51.440
Bianyifang's flavor...

00:36:51.440 --> 00:36:53.239
is something many people can't even imitate.

00:36:53.360 --> 00:36:54.719
That doesn't sound like you.

00:36:54.719 --> 00:36:56.519
You worked in a big corporation for years.

00:36:56.519 --> 00:36:58.480
You should know what differentiation is.

00:37:00.119 --> 00:37:01.159
Second question.

00:37:02.360 --> 00:37:04.519
Today's roast duck was all made by Big Brother.

00:37:05.199 --> 00:37:06.119
For over a decade now,

00:37:06.119 --> 00:37:08.159
Big Brother has rarely made roast duck himself.

00:37:08.360 --> 00:37:10.360
So let me ask Uncle Tong and Brother Dayang.

00:37:11.679 --> 00:37:14.239
What's the difference in flavor between

00:37:14.400 --> 00:37:16.440
Xiao Zhang's roast duck and Big Brother's?

00:37:25.159 --> 00:37:26.800
If you put it that way,

00:37:27.119 --> 00:37:28.760
it's nothing much.

00:37:28.760 --> 00:37:30.320
My apprentice learned it from me.

00:37:30.320 --> 00:37:31.519
Isn't it the same?

00:37:31.519 --> 00:37:33.239
My pronunciation isn't very accurate.

00:37:34.519 --> 00:37:37.480
So, since Little Zhang's skill and Big Brother's skill

00:37:37.480 --> 00:37:38.719
are exactly the same,

00:37:38.920 --> 00:37:41.400
then Big Brother lacks irreplaceability.

00:37:44.199 --> 00:37:45.840
In your business understanding,

00:37:45.840 --> 00:37:48.000
if a product can be replaced at any time,

00:37:48.119 --> 00:37:49.480
can it still have value?

00:37:52.599 --> 00:37:53.519
Third question.

00:37:53.519 --> 00:37:54.800
Why do you have so many questions?

00:37:54.800 --> 00:37:56.000
Last question.

00:37:57.760 --> 00:37:59.039
I've been gone for twenty years.

00:37:59.599 --> 00:38:00.920
This time I came back,

00:38:01.480 --> 00:38:03.159
and tasted Peng Le Xuan's roast duck.

00:38:03.679 --> 00:38:05.320
It's completely different from twenty years ago.

00:38:06.280 --> 00:38:07.599
You're all old neighbors.

00:38:07.960 --> 00:38:09.719
Uncle Tong, Brother Dayang,

00:38:10.039 --> 00:38:11.360
think about it carefully.

00:38:11.639 --> 00:38:13.559
Twenty years, thirty years,

00:38:13.719 --> 00:38:14.880
even forty years.

00:38:15.199 --> 00:38:17.119
Is the taste back then and now

00:38:17.239 --> 00:38:18.360
exactly the same?

00:38:19.920 --> 00:38:21.039
Don't mention it,

00:38:21.159 --> 00:38:23.719
I remember when Grandpa Ma was still alive,

00:38:23.840 --> 00:38:26.800
the duck he roasted seemed...

00:38:28.280 --> 00:38:30.840
it... it was a bit... not quite the same.

00:38:30.840 --> 00:38:31.679
Hold on.

00:38:31.760 --> 00:38:33.119
It's not 'seemed'.

00:38:33.119 --> 00:38:34.360
It *is* different.

00:38:34.920 --> 00:38:36.440
Uh... don't take offense.

00:38:36.440 --> 00:38:37.920
No, no, please, go on.

00:38:38.199 --> 00:38:39.599
Me, forty years ago,

00:38:39.599 --> 00:38:42.239
I came to Peng Le Xuan for the first time to eat roast duck.

00:38:42.800 --> 00:38:43.840
Back then,

00:38:43.840 --> 00:38:46.079
it was Old Master Ma who roasted it himself.

00:38:46.079 --> 00:38:47.320
He even served it.

00:38:47.320 --> 00:38:49.360
That first bite I took,

00:38:51.239 --> 00:38:52.519
that flavor...

00:38:52.719 --> 00:38:53.400
Don't even say it.

00:38:53.400 --> 00:38:54.880
I'll never forget it for the rest of my life.

00:38:54.880 --> 00:38:56.159
It was so incredibly fragrant.

00:38:56.400 --> 00:38:58.719
That flavor, unforgettable for a lifetime.

00:38:58.719 --> 00:38:59.280
Weiguo,

00:38:59.280 --> 00:39:00.920
what you're saying isn't right.

00:39:01.159 --> 00:39:03.119
The feed the ducks eat now

00:39:03.119 --> 00:39:05.360
is different from what the ducks ate in the past.

00:39:05.360 --> 00:39:06.400
The meat is different,

00:39:06.400 --> 00:39:08.000
so the taste is definitely different.

00:39:08.000 --> 00:39:09.239
Right, honey?

00:39:09.760 --> 00:39:10.840
Let me tell you,

00:39:10.840 --> 00:39:12.400
the breed of ducks nowadays

00:39:12.400 --> 00:39:14.039
is different from back in the day.

00:39:14.960 --> 00:39:16.599
Are you trying to pick a fight?

00:39:17.039 --> 00:39:18.719
Old... Old Wang, don't be angry.

00:39:19.400 --> 00:39:21.239
The world is changing, you're changing too.

00:39:21.239 --> 00:39:22.199
That's normal.

00:39:23.960 --> 00:39:24.559
You...

00:39:37.679 --> 00:39:38.519
Yuanyuan.

00:39:38.800 --> 00:39:39.920
Dad!

00:39:39.920 --> 00:39:41.079
Xuanxuan, quick, quick, come here!

00:39:41.079 --> 00:39:42.079
Auntie Liang!

00:39:42.079 --> 00:39:43.480
Hello, Auntie Liang.

00:39:43.480 --> 00:39:44.440
Hello, Yuanyuan.

00:39:44.559 --> 00:39:45.039
Let's go.

00:39:45.039 --> 00:39:46.360
Mr. Li, hello.

00:39:46.360 --> 00:39:48.400
I'm Xuanxuan's aunt.

00:39:48.800 --> 00:39:49.960
Um, Mr. Li,

00:39:49.960 --> 00:39:51.599
our family suddenly has an emergency.

00:39:51.599 --> 00:39:52.800
I have to go back right away.

00:39:52.800 --> 00:39:53.440
But,

00:39:53.440 --> 00:39:55.000
Miss Dong is at the company.

00:39:55.000 --> 00:39:56.559
I can't reach her right now.

00:39:56.760 --> 00:40:00.280
Do you think... could you help look after Xuanxuan for me?

00:40:00.280 --> 00:40:01.880
No problem, leave it to me.

00:40:02.480 --> 00:40:03.599
Thank you, thank you so much.

00:40:03.599 --> 00:40:04.119
Go take care of your business.

00:40:04.119 --> 00:40:05.519
Xuanxuan, listen to Uncle, okay?

00:40:05.519 --> 00:40:06.400
Alright then, thanks, goodbye.

00:40:06.400 --> 00:40:07.239
No problem, no problem.

00:40:07.480 --> 00:40:09.639
So, Xuanxuan, Yuanyuan,

00:40:10.079 --> 00:40:11.440
do you want to eat first,

00:40:11.440 --> 00:40:12.320
or play first?

00:40:12.559 --> 00:40:15.360
Mom assigned me homework.

00:40:15.360 --> 00:40:18.880
Math Olympiad, programming, and English.

00:40:19.159 --> 00:40:21.000
What's wrong with your mom?

00:40:21.000 --> 00:40:22.039
The hardships she suffered as a child,

00:40:22.039 --> 00:40:23.400
she's now piling them all on you.

00:40:23.639 --> 00:40:25.920
Mom is doing it for my own good.

00:40:26.960 --> 00:40:28.760
Mom assigned me homework too.

00:40:28.760 --> 00:40:32.119
Piano, drawing, and English.

00:40:33.239 --> 00:40:34.119
My head is spinning.

00:40:34.960 --> 00:40:36.119
Today, listen to me.

00:40:36.119 --> 00:40:37.119
Forget about all that.

00:40:37.119 --> 00:40:38.320
Let's play first. Let's go!

00:40:38.400 --> 00:40:38.960
Let's go!

00:40:39.920 --> 00:40:40.519
Careful!

00:40:44.639 --> 00:40:45.800
Listen up, Boss Dong.

00:40:46.320 --> 00:40:47.880
Your son is currently in my custody.

00:40:48.039 --> 00:40:50.280
I advise you to drop your work immediately

00:40:50.400 --> 00:40:51.880
and come to the small square in front of the Drum Tower.

00:40:51.880 --> 00:40:54.000
Pick up your son at the second bench.

00:40:54.199 --> 00:40:56.119
If you're late, you'll bear the consequences.

00:40:56.800 --> 00:40:57.559
That's all.

00:41:01.960 --> 00:41:02.920
Hello, sir.

00:41:02.920 --> 00:41:04.599
How can I help you today?

00:41:04.719 --> 00:41:06.000
I'm looking at bags.

00:41:06.199 --> 00:41:06.639
Alright.

00:41:06.639 --> 00:41:08.360
It just so happens we got a new shipment in.

00:41:08.360 --> 00:41:09.519
Shall I introduce them to you?

00:41:09.519 --> 00:41:10.440
Thanks.

00:41:11.039 --> 00:41:13.320
You know our store doesn't offer discounts, right?

00:41:14.320 --> 00:41:14.960
Sir,

00:41:15.159 --> 00:41:16.440
may I ask,

00:41:16.440 --> 00:41:18.519
what do you do for a living?

00:41:19.159 --> 00:41:21.639
I work at a bank.

00:41:23.039 --> 00:41:26.239
And who are you looking to buy this bag for?

00:41:26.239 --> 00:41:27.400
My wife.

00:41:29.000 --> 00:41:30.400
Let me introduce this one to you.

00:41:30.599 --> 00:41:33.239
This model is our store's versatile bag.

00:41:33.239 --> 00:41:35.320
It suits your demeanor perfectly.

00:41:35.320 --> 00:41:36.679
And it would also be very fitting for your wife.

00:41:36.679 --> 00:41:37.320
How about this:

00:41:37.320 --> 00:41:38.719
Let me take it out for you to see.

00:41:38.719 --> 00:41:40.280
No, no, no, it's fine, it's fine, no need.

00:41:40.280 --> 00:41:42.280
I'll... I'll just look around first. Thank you.

00:41:42.960 --> 00:41:43.559
Okay.